## Troubleshooting

<details>
<summary>""Command not found"" after installation</summary>

Ensure `vestige-mcp` is in your PATH:
```bash
which vestige-mcp
# Or use the full path:
claude mcp add vestige /usr/local/bin/vestige-mcp -s user
```
