# Optimized High Resolution 3D Dense-U-Net for Brain and Spine Segmentation

<p align=""center"">
  <a href=""https://www.mdpi.com/2076-3417/9/3/404""><img src=""https://img.shields.io/badge/Paper-Applied%20Sciences%20(2019)-blue""></a>
