2. Click 'Start Quiz' to begin. The quiz will pick 40 random questions.
3. Answer questions (one at a time). Click Submit at the end to see your score.
4. You can retake to get a new random set of 40 questions.

Hosting:
- You can host the files on GitHub Pages, Netlify, or open index.html locally on your device.
