S Gold, B Christian, S Arndt, G Zeien, T Cizadlo, DL Johnson, M Flaum, and NC Andreasen. Functional MRI statistical software packages: a comparative analysis. Human Brain Mapping, 6:73-84, 1998.

### dcm2niix  

